  <article class="prose">
    <span class="last-updated">Last updated: June 2025</span>

    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p>Real Tip Calculator is a 100% free online tip calculator — no ads, no accounts, no downloads required. Built for anyone who wants to calculate the perfect tip instantly.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      We built Real Tip Calculator with one goal in mind: make tipping simple, fair, and stress-free for everyone.
      Whether you're at a restaurant, a nail salon, a hair salon, a tattoo parlor, or tipping a DoorDash driver — the
      mental math can be awkward, especially when you're splitting a bill with a group. We wanted to solve that problem
      with a tool that's faster and smarter than a basic Google tip calculator.
    </p>

    <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
    <p>Unlike a plain percentage calculator, Real Tip Calculator was designed to guide you to the <em>right</em> tip — not just any tip:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Service Quality Slider</strong> — Rate your experience from Poor to Excellent, and our calculator automatically suggests the appropriate tip percentage. No more guessing.</li>
      <li><strong>Smart Bill Splitting</strong> — Enter the number of people in your group and instantly see each person's share of the bill and tip, broken down clearly.</li>
      <li><strong>Round-Up Feature</strong> — We suggest rounding your total to the nearest $5 for clean, easy cash payments.</li>
      <li><strong>30+ Country Tipping Guide</strong> — Tipping customs vary wildly around the world. We cover more than 30 countries with local customs and expected percentages.</li>
      <li><strong>Works on Any Device</strong> — Real Tip Calculator works perfectly on iPhone, Android, desktop, and tablet. No app download needed — just open it in your browser.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
    <p>
      The tools we found were either too basic (just a number × percentage), too cluttered with ads, or
      required a sign-up. We wanted something clean, fast, and actually helpful — a tip calculator app experience
      right in the browser. So we built it ourselves and made it free for everyone, forever.
    </p>

    <h2>Completely Free — Forever</h2>
    <p>
      Real Tip Calculator is and always will be free to use. There are no premium plans, no paywalls, and
      no signup requirements. We believe that basic financial tools should be accessible to everyone.
    </p>

